' Main Application
note right of MainActivity
  Entry point of the application.
  Handles lifecycle and initial setup.
end note

' ViewModels
note right of GameViewModel
  Manages game state and logic for all game variants:
  - Handles dice rolling and scoring
  - Manages player turns and game flow
  - Coordinates between UI and game managers
  - Handles game statistics and analysis
end note

note right of AppViewModel
  Manages application-wide state:
  - User authentication state
  - Profile management
  - Interface mode settings
end note

' Managers
note right of StatisticsManager
  Analyzes and tracks player performance:
  - Calculates win rates and trends
  - Manages player analytics
  - Updates leaderboard data
end note

note right of DiceManager
  Handles dice-related operations:
  - Manages dice rolling mechanics
  - Controls dice state and animations
  - Handles shake-to-roll functionality
end note

' Repositories
note right of AuthRepository
  Manages authentication operations:
  - Email/password authentication
  - Google Sign-In
  - User session management
end note


@enduml